snippet.textDisplay: How about somebody in the media asks the PM or any of these other Government 'officials' if they understand the difference in Relative Risk Reduction and Absolute Risk Reduction when it comes to the vaccines efficacy.  The vaccine manufacturers use 'Relative Risk Reduction' numbers for their study publications because that's where they can use numbers like 95%, and the Government pushes that as though it were true. But RRR is NOT what people are led (lied) to believe. It relates to one group versus another placebo group in a controlled study only.  Absolute Risk Reduction applies to a persons individual chance of not being infected if they are vaccinated.  And with Pfizer, the ARR number is around 0.8%.  THAT is why so many people who are double and triple vaxxed are getting sick...  and THAT is why so many people think that mandating vaccines and punishing healthy people who don't want them is a scientifically illiterate and monumentally stupid idea.

snippet.textDisplay:
The protesters chanting free Novak might have chanted free No Vaxx - his medical 
exemption reasons he refused to reveal for a while and then turns out the two medical officers who signed off did so because The Joker had already had Covid and so could not be vaxxed.  There is plenty of footage of him participating in several settings while he actually had Covid.  I do not believe for one single minute that he should not be sent home - The fact is he wants to play in order to win Aus Open is because he wants to win all 3 grand slams this year to beat Roger and Nadal and their 20 record.  This is all a joke. He is not a god. his ego is overtaking all semblance of decency and the higher good of caring for others. I used to like him and he is a great player - but playing Covid rules is low.
